{"tid":1679220,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對抗直升機戰","createTime":"2019-10-28T05:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T02:53:50.000Z","uid":295487,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8e98d9953ba73a4fe94c892313b6924f229b26","tid":1679220,"uid":295487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:34:37.000Z","msg":"1.逃跑時盡量走上行人路及橫街。因為直升機在高空衹會清楚見到馬路情況，行人路尤其是橫街是有樓遮蔽着。<br />\n<br />\n2. 黑夜作戰較有利，因為衣着同頭盔都是黑色，較難偵測。<br />\n<br />\n3.警方最怕是人多，所以除佐主場設road block, 走散佐之後就唔好在其他地方設road block,因為在上空好清楚看到交通情況，所以警車可以多方面包圍!<br />\n<br />\n大家還有什麼建議，可以互相觀摩!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576e1f895b80856338a0e26c71736344aedd6eee","tid":1679220,"uid":156096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:34:51.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽 5毛大軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD50oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=b89ed796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"4fd8e83f1b866076a0ef23e171a780f62e596e9b","tid":1679220,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:35:15.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2ab9d9d5e2bdab2131ef7c7a06472e22be2ac5","tid":1679220,"uid":3865,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"rep